  "texts": [
    "Note that subclasses Sst Chodl, Chandelier and Lamp5 Lhx6 were not annotated in the MERFISH dataset and were removed from the DART-FISH analysis for consistency.",
    "The rest of the analysis was carried out with 242 shared genes between the datasets (bottom panel of Supplementary Fig. 5c).",
    "Annotating the kidney data set.",
    "Cells with less than 5 and more than 100 transcripts were filtered (2024 out of 65565).",
    "The top 250 highly variable genes were kept for downstream analyses (scanpy.experimental.pp.highly_variable_gene(., flavor='pearson_residuals'))."
